  "title": "Compliance Officer",
  "description": "<p>*MAS Reporting</p><p>*Review financial reporting and handle Auditor and Tax agent<br /><br />Key responsibilities</p><p>1.\tDevelop, implement, and maintain compliance policies, procedures, and frameworks</p><p>2.\tConduct compliance monitoring and internal audits to assess adherence to regulatory requirements</p><p>3.\tLiaise with regulators, auditors, and external consultants when required.</p><p>4.\tPrepare and review regulatory reports and filings, annual declaration, including MAS returns</p><p>5.\tConduct in review of customer due diligence (CDD) processes, anti-money laundering (AML) compliance, and risk assessments</p><p>6.\tConduct compliance training sessions to enhance awareness of regulatory requirements</p><p>7.\tMonitor and interpret changes in regulatory guidelines, compliance adjustment</p><p></p><p>Required Qualifications & skills</p><p>1.\tExperience in a financial services regulatory compliance/internal audit role/fund management industry</p><p>2.\tKnowledge of MAS regulations</p><p>3.\tAbility and willingness to research regulations independently</p><p>4.\tFamiliarity with AML/CFT regulations and customer due diligence processes</p>",
