    "description": "<p>SOFOS is a fund management company, regulated by Monetary Authority of Singapore (MAS). We hold a Capital Market Services Licence under the Securities and Futures Act (Cap. 289) to conduct regulated activities in Fund Management for only accredited investor or institutional investor as defined in Section 4A of the <a href=\"https://sso.agc.gov.sg/Act/SFA2001#pr4A-\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SFA</a></p>\n<p>SOFOS has 2 core businesses:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://sofos.com.sg/solutions-services/managed-accounts/\"><strong>Managed Accounts (EAM Business)</strong></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://sofos.com.sg/solutions-services/fund-management/\"><strong>Fund Management (PE funds – Real Estate, Infrastructure, distress assets)</strong></a></li>\n</ul>",
